    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/22257a6c15761a41be75acf30b43d8b5.avif?t=1771842007\" width=616 height=322 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不要眨眼！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Versus in the Dark》是一款高速平台格斗游戏，所有人都是隐形的！小心脚下，留意敌人，否则你会被暗影中的一击劈成两半！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/11b618404dff0540df79bc37c7b32abd.poster.avif?t=1771842007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/11b618404dff0540df79bc37c7b32abd.webm?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/11b618404dff0540df79bc37c7b32abd.mp4?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEE, SLASH &amp; DISAPPEAR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏自己并利用环境陷阱对手。但要小心——雷电、闪烁的灯光、积雪或一扇门都可能暴露你的位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/1c446522e7615df59fab1a7b303432d5.poster.avif?t=1771842007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/1c446522e7615df59fab1a7b303432d5.webm?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/1c446522e7615df59fab1a7b303432d5.mp4?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单却深邃</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三键操作，无连招，无血条——一击必杀！上手容易，人人都能享受。掌握隐身之术，在融合平台、潜行与光剑武士刀的战略对战中取胜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/e9324332b0935444b25d21f08e1eb62f.poster.avif?t=1771842007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/e9324332b0935444b25d21f08e1eb62f.webm?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/e9324332b0935444b25d21f08e1eb62f.mp4?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ONLINE + LOCAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多4名玩家，可自由混战或组队！与好友或全球玩家对战，感受成为最后幸存者的快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/a17c2c61640e79416378b32d20a534d2.poster.avif?t=1771842007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/a17c2c61640e79416378b32d20a534d2.webm?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064240/extras/a17c2c61640e79416378b32d20a534d2.mp4?t=1771842007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥷 扮演 INVISIBLE NINJA，在独特的平台格斗游戏中用陷阱击败对手。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹️ 上手容易，精通困难。 人人都能快速享受乐趣！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 时尚的 像素艺术风格，融合日本封建与街头文化，霓虹灯点亮的鸟居别具魅力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👺 用丰富的 面具与帽子 自定义忍者，在 50张地图 上展开战斗并保持隐身。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌐 最后幸存者、夺灯、团队模式… 多达 5种可自定义模式，支持 在线与本地 对战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗡️ 光剑武士刀 —— 因为普通的太无聊了？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地多人游戏需要使用手柄。支持 <strong>Xbox、PlayStation、Switch</strong> 等多种手柄。</p>",
